               <p>I was buying some peas in the <placeName id="t17780715-8-crimeloc37">Fleet-market</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17780715-8-crimeloc37" type="placeName" value="Fleet-market"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17780715-8-crimeloc37" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780715-8-off35 t17780715-8-crimeloc37"></join> on the 18th of June; I felt the prisoner's hand in my pocket; I turned, and saw my handkerchief in the prisoner's hand; he was going to put it into his pocket. I secured him, and delivered him and the handkerchief to the constable. I saw the prisoner drop the handkerchief behind him, and I took it up.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780715-8-person188">
                  WILLIAM
                   MARTIN
               <interp inst="t17780715-8-person188" type="surname" value="MARTIN"></interp>
