                     <interp inst="t17780715-8-person188" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a constable; I received the prisoner and the handkerchief from the prosecutor.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>As I was going home, they laid hold of me; this gentleman said I had picked his pocket; I never touched his pocket; I have not a friend in the world.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17780715-8-verdict38" type="verdictDescription">
